<release>
  <module>gst-python</module>
  <module-fancy>GStreamer Python bindings</module-fancy>
  <name>Ninety Tons of Thunder</name>
  <version>0.10.22</version>

  <intro>

<p>
The GStreamer team is proud to announce a new release
in the 0.10.x stable series of the
GStreamer Python Bindings.
</p>
<p>
The 0.10.x series is a stable series targeted at end users.
</p>

  </intro>
  <features>
    <feature>pad probes working properly with recent GStreamer</feature>
    <feature>fixes for encoding profiles and encodebin</feature>
    <feature>build fixes</feature>
    <feature>install pygst.h, pygstminiobject.h and other headers so they can be used by other python bindings such the ones for gstreamer-editing-services</feature>
  </features>

